<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Diwali Wishes</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styling */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-image: url('https://img.freepik.com/premium-photo/happy-diwali-traditional-indian-festival-diwali-festival-holiday-design-generative-ai_756405-2859.jpg'); /* Diwali-themed image URL */
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Dark Overlay */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Adjust opacity to control darkness */
            z-index: 0;
        }

        /* Diwali Heading */
        .diwali-heading {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #ffda79;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 218, 121, 0.7), 0 0 20px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.9);
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: glowPulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Glow Animation */
        @keyframes glowPulse {
            0%, 100% {
                text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 218, 121, 0.7), 0 0 30px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.9), 0 0 45px rgba(255, 87, 34, 1);
            }
            50% {
                text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 218, 121, 1), 0 0 35px rgba(255, 140, 0, 1), 0 0 60px rgba(255, 87, 34, 1);
            }
        }

        /* Wishes Container */
        .wishes-container {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .wishes-container p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        /* Custom Button */
        .send-wish-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff9800, #ff5722);
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 5px 15px rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.4);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .send-wish-btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff5722, #ff9800);
            box-shadow: 0px 8px 20px rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.6);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Responsive Styling */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .diwali-heading {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            .wishes-container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .wishes-container p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            .send-wish-btn {
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Diwali Wishes Section -->
    <h1 class="diwali-heading">✨ Happy Diwali ✨</h1>
    <div class="wishes-container">
        <p>Wishing you and your loved ones a bright and joyful Diwali! May this festival of lights bring happiness, prosperity, and love to your home.</p>
        <p>May every diya you light shine prosperity and health into your life. Here's to a Diwali filled with love, laughter, and endless blessings!</p>
        
        <!-- Send Wishes Button -->
        <a href="#" class="send-wish-btn">Send Diwali Wishes</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
